00:02:46.570 --> 00:02:50.531
- My bike weighs in at 7.3 kilos
and that's with a Garmin Virb

00:02:50.531 --> 00:02:54.348
on the handlebars, obviously.
With a bottle, it takes it up to 7.875,

00:02:54.348 --> 00:02:59.753
then with the ballast, it weighs
in at a pretty hefty 9.8 kilograms.

00:03:04.885 --> 00:03:07.894
♪ [music] ♪

00:03:14.671 --> 00:03:19.700
